snippet.title: Claire's Cruising Cafe: High Seas Cuisine Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Alawar Entertainment needs a world-class chef like you in the latest addition to the Claire’s Cruisin’ Café series!

With your chef's knife in hand and the tropical sun at your back, it's time to create culinary sensations for the passengers of a luxury ocean liner! From mouth-watering meatballs to succulent sushi, it's a race against the clock to win the contest of serving the most customers. Luckily, you won't have to do it alone! Work with old friends to conquer new challenges and unravel a puzzling mystery while crafting the finest cuisine on the seven seas! Are you ready to chart new waters for the adventure of a lifetime? Find out in Claire's Cruisin' Cafe': High Seas!

Download the Free Trial for PC!
